    "With the increasing complexity and size of port systems and terminal infrastructures, the digital twin can be a valuable tool for increasing transparency, improving performance and reducing complexity.",
    "However, further advancements in the field are necessary to fully realize the potential of strict digital twins in ports and container terminals.",
